## 🌍 What is a Community Development System?

It’s a platform where users (e.g. residents, officials, admins) can:

* 📝 Submit needs/issues (e.g., bad roads, water problems)
* 👀 Track ongoing development projects
* 📢 Get updates or announcements from community admins
* 💬 Discuss or comment on issues/projects
* 📊 Admins manage users, feedback, and development data

---

## 💡 Suggested Features Breakdown

### 👥 User Roles

* **Admin** – manages everything
* **Project Manager** – creates & updates community projects
* **User/Resident** – submits issues, comments, views updates

---

### 📋 Key Modules

| Module            | Description                                         |
| ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| 🛠️ Projects      | Add/update development projects (e.g., Road Repair) |
| 📨 Issues         | Residents submit local issues or complaints         |
| 📢 Announcements  | Admin can send community-wide updates               |
| 💬 Comments       | On both projects & issues                           |
| 🧾 Reports        | Show resolved vs unresolved issues                  |
| 🔒 Authentication | Login/Register + role-based access                  |

